  ['Universal intent','Describe the outcome once; Madeus preserves it through every system and handoff.'],
  ['Best-capability routing','Models, agents, tools, and people compete on quality, privacy, speed, and cost.'],
  ['Governed execution','Evidence, permissions, approvals, rollback, and signed receipts travel with every action.'],
  ['Independent verification','Builders never grade their own work; separate checks prove behavior and outcome.'],
  ['Compounding memory','Decisions become reusable precedent instead of another transcript nobody can find.'],
]
